`(?=1(0{2,}+)(?!$))1` - `?=1(0{2,}+)` positive lookahead: 1 followed by a capturing group for the sequence of at least 2 zeroes

`(?!$)` - negative lookahead - group of 0s not followed by the end of the string
1 - closing 1

